                            <incipit>
                                <locus>F.1 </locus>śrīgaṇeśāya namaḥ || hariḥ om || || hiraṇyavarṇāṃ
                                hariṇīṃ suvarṇarajatasrajām || caṃdrāṃ hiraṇmayīṃ lakṣmīṃ jātavedo
                                mam āvaha || </incipit>
                            <explicit>
                                <locus>F.2v </locus>śrīvarcasvam āyuṣyam ārogyam ā[ro]vidhā
                                chubhamānai mahīyate || dhānyaṃ dhanaṃ paśuṃ bahuputralābhaṃ
                                śatasaṃvatsaraṃ dīrgham āyuḥ || iti śrīsūkta samāptaḥ || śrī
                                kṛṣṇārpaṇam astu || śrīsāmbha caraṇa raj || idaṃ likhitaṃ ity
                                upanāmakamasūkaramahā-deveṇa likhitaṃ || </explicit>
                        </msItem>

